Date: Fri, 10 Jul 2026 05:31:56 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 2/3] Add unit test suite and requirements.txt

Covers the pure logic paths that don't need root/raw sockets:
- classify_exposure() web/SSH detection, incl. a regression test for
  the banner-vs-port bug fixed in the previous commit
- banner parsing / product-version extraction (Apache, nginx, OpenSSH)
- OpenSSH version normalization for CVE matching
- TTL-based OS fingerprinting heuristic
- target validation, with DNS resolution mocked

26 tests, all passing. Scanning/packet logic itself still needs manual
integration testing since it requires raw socket privileges.
